<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type">
	</head>
	<body style="font-size:15px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family:  Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; height: auto;">
		<div style="font-weight:bold; font-size:20px;"><span style="color:#55aad4;">Message from</span> Trade<span style="color:#55aad4;">Ya</span><br/></div>

		<p>Dear <%=@user.first_name.capitalize %>,</p>

		<p>What do you think about taking it to the next level? By becoming a member, you get to keep trading with awesome folks like you.<p><br/>
			
		<p><a href="<%=home_url%>?guest_user_signup=true&guest_user_token=<%=@user.guest_user_token%>"><img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/tradeya_prod/tradeya/images/sign_me_up.png" onmouseover="this.src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/tradeya_prod/tradeya/images/sign_me_up_roll.png';" onmouseout="this.src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/tradeya_prod/tradeya/images/sign_me_up.png';" alt="Sign Me Up!"/></a></p>

		<p>Remember, your Guest account will only be active for <span><%= (@user.guest_days_left < 1)? "1" : @user.guest_days_left.to_s %> more day<%= (@user.guest_days_left <= 1) ? "" : "s"%>!</span></p>
		
		<p>Cheers,</p>
		<p>Jared TradeYa</p><br/>
		<p>If you don't want anymore of these emails, <a href="<%=guest_deactivate_account_url%>?guest_user_token=<%=@user.guest_user_token %>">click here to unsubscribe</a> from your TradeYa Guest account.</p>
	</body>
</html>